		</p>
		
		<div class='grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6'>
			<!-- Top Cryptanalysis Projects -->
			<div class='card bg-base-100 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow'>
				<div class='card-body'>
					<h2 class='card-title'>
						<svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
			<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M12.316 3.051a1 1 0 01.633 1.265l-4 12a1 1 0 11-1.898-.632l4-12a1 1 0 011.265-.633zM5.707 6.293a1 1 0 010 1.414L3.414 10l2.293 2.293a1 1 0 11-1.414 1.414l-3-3a1 1 0 010-1.414l3-3a1 1 0 011.414 0zm8.586 0a1 1 0 011.414 0l3 3a1 1 0 010 1.414l-3 3a1 1 0 11-1.414-1.414L16.586 10l-2.293-2.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
		</svg>
						Autoguess
					</h2>
					<p>An easy-to-use, general and open-source tool to solve the guess-and-determine problem</p>
					<div class='flex gap-2 mt-3 mb-2'>
						<div class='badge badge-primary'>★ 28</div>
						<div class='badge badge-outline'>Python</div>
						<div class='badge badge-outline'>Blockcipher</div>
					</div>
					<div class='card-actions justify-between'>
						<div class='text-xs text-gray-500'>Published: ACNS 2022</div>
						<a href='https://github.com/hadipourh/autoguess' target='_blank' class='btn btn-primary btn-sm'>View Code</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class='card bg-base-100 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow'>
				<div class='card-body'>
					<h2 class='card-title'>
						<svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
			<path d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
		</svg>
						Sboxanalyzer
					</h2>
					<p>An easy-to-use and open-source tool for differential, linear, differential-linear, and integral analysis of S-boxes</p>
					<div class='flex gap-2 mt-3 mb-2'>
						<div class='badge badge-primary'>★ 30</div>
						<div class='badge badge-outline'>C</div>
						<div class='badge badge-outline'>Ddlct</div>
					</div>
					<div class='card-actions justify-between'>
						<div class='text-xs text-gray-500'>Research Tool</div>
						<a href='https://github.com/hadipourh/sboxanalyzer' target='_blank' class='btn btn-primary btn-sm'>View Code</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class='card bg-base-100 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow'>
				<div class='card-body'>
					<h2 class='card-title'>
						<svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
			<path d="M13 6a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zM18 8a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM14 15a4 4 0 00-8 0v3h8v-3z"></path>
		</svg>
						Course Cryptanalysis
					</h2>
					<p>A Course in Cryptanalysis</p>
					<div class='flex gap-2 mt-3 mb-2'>
						<div class='badge badge-primary'>★ 144</div>
						<div class='badge badge-outline'>TeX</div>
						
					</div>
					<div class='card-actions justify-between'>
						<div class='text-xs text-gray-500'>Educational Resource</div>
						<a href='https://github.com/hadipourh/course-cryptanalysis' target='_blank' class='btn btn-primary btn-sm'>View Code</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class='card bg-base-100 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow'>
				<div class='card-body'>
					<h2 class='card-title'>
						<svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
			<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M12.316 3.051a1 1 0 01.633 1.265l-4 12a1 1 0 11-1.898-.632l4-12a1 1 0 011.265-.633zM5.707 6.293a1 1 0 010 1.414L3.414 10l2.293 2.293a1 1 0 11-1.414 1.414l-3-3a1 1 0 010-1.414l3-3a1 1 0 011.414 0zm8.586 0a1 1 0 011.414 0l3 3a1 1 0 010 1.414l-3 3a1 1 0 11-1.414-1.414L16.586 10l-2.293-2.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
		</svg>
						Zeroplus
					</h2>
					<p>Improved Search for Integral, Impossible Differential and Zero-Correlation Attacks: Application to Ascon, ForkSKINNY, SKINNY, MANTIS, PRESENT and QARMAv2</p>
					<div class='flex gap-2 mt-3 mb-2'>
						<div class='badge badge-primary'>★ 13</div>
						<div class='badge badge-outline'>MiniZinc</div>
						<div class='badge badge-outline'>Ascon</div>
					</div>
					<div class='card-actions justify-between'>
						<div class='text-xs text-gray-500'>Published: FSE 2024</div>
						<a href='https://github.com/hadipourh/zeroplus' target='_blank' class='btn btn-primary btn-sm'>View Code</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class='card bg-base-100 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow'>
				<div class='card-body'>
					<h2 class='card-title'>
						<svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
			<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M12.316 3.051a1 1 0 01.633 1.265l-4 12a1 1 0 11-1.898-.632l4-12a1 1 0 011.265-.633zM5.707 6.293a1 1 0 010 1.414L3.414 10l2.293 2.293a1 1 0 11-1.414 1.414l-3-3a1 1 0 010-1.414l3-3a1 1 0 011.414 0zm8.586 0a1 1 0 011.414 0l3 3a1 1 0 010 1.414l-3 3a1 1 0 11-1.414-1.414L16.586 10l-2.293-2.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
		</svg>
						Zero
					</h2>
					<p>An Automatic Tool to Search for Full Impossible-Differential, Zero-Correlation and Integral Attacks</p>
					<div class='flex gap-2 mt-3 mb-2'>
						<div class='badge badge-primary'>★ 11</div>
						<div class='badge badge-outline'>Python</div>
						<div class='badge badge-outline'>Block Cipher</div>
