					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class='card bg-base-100 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow'>
				<div class='card-body'>
					<h2 class='card-title'>
						<svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
		<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M3 4a1 1 0 011-1h12a1 1 0 110 2H4a1 1 0 01-1-1zm0 4a1 1 0 011-1h12a1 1 0 110 2H4a1 1 0 01-1-1zm0 4a1 1 0 011-1h12a1 1 0 110 2H4a1 1 0 01-1-1zm0 4a1 1 0 011-1h12a1 1 0 110 2H4a1 1 0 01-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
	</svg>
						Ctiming
					</h2>
					<p>Measuring the Performance of C Implementations in CPU clock cycle</p>
					<div class='flex gap-2 mt-3 mb-2'>
						<div class='badge badge-primary'>★ 11</div>
						<div class='badge badge-outline'>C</div>
						<div class='badge badge-outline'>Aes</div>
					</div>
					<div class='card-actions justify-between'>
						<div class='text-xs text-gray-500'>Research Tool</div>
						<a href='https://github.com/hadipourh/ctiming' target='_blank' class='btn btn-primary btn-sm'>View Code</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class='card bg-base-100 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow'>
				<div class='card-body'>
					<h2 class='card-title'>
						<svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
		<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M3 4a1 1 0 011-1h12a1 1 0 110 2H4a1 1 0 01-1-1zm0 4a1 1 0 011-1h12a1 1 0 110 2H4a1 1 0 01-1-1zm0 4a1 1 0 011-1h12a1 1 0 110 2H4a1 1 0 01-1-1zm0 4a1 1 0 011-1h12a1 1 0 110 2H4a1 1 0 01-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
	</svg>
						DL
					</h2>
					<p>Revisiting Differential-Linear Attacks via a Boomerang Perspective</p>
					<div class='flex gap-2 mt-3 mb-2'>
						<div class='badge badge-primary'>★ 10</div>
						<div class='badge badge-outline'>Python</div>
						<div class='badge badge-outline'>Aes</div>
					</div>
					<div class='card-actions justify-between'>
						<div class='text-xs text-gray-500'>Published: CRYPTO 2024</div>
						<a href='https://github.com/hadipourh/DL' target='_blank' class='btn btn-primary btn-sm'>View Code</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class='card bg-base-100 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow'>
				<div class='card-body'>
					<h2 class='card-title'>
						<svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
		<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M3 4a1 1 0 011-1h12a1 1 0 110 2H4a1 1 0 01-1-1zm0 4a1 1 0 011-1h12a1 1 0 110 2H4a1 1 0 01-1-1zm0 4a1 1 0 011-1h12a1 1 0 110 2H4a1 1 0 01-1-1zm0 4a1 1 0 011-1h12a1 1 0 110 2H4a1 1 0 01-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
	</svg>
						Boomerang
					</h2>
					<p>A New Method to Search for Boomerang Distinguishers: Improved Rectangle Attacks on SKINNY and CRAFT</p>
					<div class='flex gap-2 mt-3 mb-2'>
						<div class='badge badge-primary'>★ 8</div>
						<div class='badge badge-outline'>Jupyter Notebook</div>
						<div class='badge badge-outline'>Automated Cryptanalysis</div>
					</div>
					<div class='card-actions justify-between'>
						<div class='text-xs text-gray-500'>Published: FSE 2022</div>
						<a href='https://github.com/hadipourh/Boomerang' target='_blank' class='btn btn-primary btn-sm'>View Code</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class='card bg-base-100 shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-shadow'>
				<div class='card-body'>
					<h2 class='card-title'>
						<svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
		<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M3 4a1 1 0 011-1h12a1 1 0 110 2H4a1 1 0 01-1-1zm0 4a1 1 0 011-1h12a1 1 0 110 2H4a1 1 0 01-1-1zm0 4a1 1 0 011-1h12a1 1 0 110 2H4a1 1 0 01-1-1zm0 4a1 1 0 011-1h12a1 1 0 110 2H4a1 1 0 01-1-1z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
	</svg>
						Talks
					</h2>
					<p>The LaTex Sources for My Talks</p>
					<div class='flex gap-2 mt-3 mb-2'>
						<div class='badge badge-primary'>★ 6</div>
						<div class='badge badge-outline'>TeX</div>
						
					</div>
					<div class='card-actions justify-between'>
						<div class='text-xs text-gray-500'>Presentation Templates</div>
						<a href='https://github.com/hadipourh/talks' target='_blank' class='btn btn-primary btn-sm'>View Code</a>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div></div>
		
		<div class='mt-12'>
			<h2 class='text-2xl font-bold mb-6'>Additional Tools & Resources</h2>
			<div class='grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6'>
				<div class='card bg-base-100 shadow-xl'>
					<div class='card-body'>
						<h3 class='card-title text-lg'>Development Tools</h3>
						<ul class='list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-sm'>
							<li><a href='https://github.com/hadipourh/KeeLoq' target='_blank' class='text-primary hover:underline'>KeeLoq</a> - C implementation of KeeLoq algorithm, equipped with a function to generate algebraic equations of KeeLoq over GF(2)</li>
							<li><a href='https://github.com/hadipourh/AES-VHDL' target='_blank' class='text-primary hover:underline'>AES VHDL</a> - VHDL Implementation of AES Algorithm</li>
							<li><a href='https://github.com/hadipourh/CryptoHDL' target='_blank' class='text-primary hover:underline'>CryptoHDL</a> - A list of VHDL codes implementing cryptographic algorithms</li>
							<li><a href='https://github.com/hadipourh/twinkle' target='_blank' class='text-primary hover:underline'>Twinkle</a> - 𝐁𝐫𝐞𝐚𝐤𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐭𝐡𝐞 𝐓𝐰𝐢𝐧𝐤𝐥𝐞 𝐀𝐮𝐭𝐡𝐞𝐧𝐭𝐢𝐜𝐚𝐭𝐞𝐝 𝐄𝐧𝐜𝐫𝐲𝐩𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧 𝐒𝐜𝐡𝐞𝐦𝐞</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
				
				<div class='card bg-base-100 shadow-xl'>
					<div class='card-body'>
						<h3 class='card-title text-lg'>Installation & Utilities</h3>
						<ul class='list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-sm'>
							<li><a href='https://github.com/hadipourh/logic-minimization' target='_blank' class='text-primary hover:underline'>Logic Minimization</a> - A repository containing off-the-shelf programs for solving the logic minimization problem</li>
							<li><a href='https://github.com/hadipourh/CTC2-Fast-Algebraic-Attack' target='_blank' class='text-primary hover:underline'>CTC2 Fast Algebraic Attack</a> - A python class implementing the Courtois Toy Cipher (CTC2) equipped with some methods for algebraic cryptanalysis of CTC2</li>
							<li><a href='https://github.com/hadipourh/craftanalysis' target='_blank' class='text-primary hover:underline'>Craftanalysis</a> - Comprehensive Security Analysis of CRAFT</li>
							<li><a href='https://github.com/hadipourh/CRAFT-Integral-Distinguisher' target='_blank' class='text-primary hover:underline'>CRAFT Integral Distinguisher</a> - Using an MILP method to find integral distinguisher based on division property for CRAFT</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>>
		
		<div class='mt-12'>
			<h2 class='text-2xl font-bold mb-4'>GitHub Integration</h2>
			<div class='card bg-base-100 shadow-xl'>
				<div class='card-body'>
					<h3 class='card-title'>Automated Content Updates</h3>
					<p class='text-gray-600 mb-4'>
						This page displays all my major cryptanalysis projects and tools. 
						The content will be automatically synchronized with my GitHub repositories for future updates.
						Star counts and repository information are fetched from the GitHub API.
					</p>
					<div class='flex gap-2'>
						<div class='badge badge-success'>GitHub API</div>
						<div class='badge badge-outline'>Auto-updated</div>
						<a href='https://github.com/hadipourh' target='_blank' class='btn btn-primary btn-sm'>View All Repositories</a>
